#include<iostream>
#include<vector>
#include<cstdio>
#include<algorithm>
using namespace std;
int main()
{
    int t,i,elem,countm;
    t=10;
    while(t--)
    {
        countm=10;
        vector<int> v(10);
        for(i=0;i<10;i++)
        {
            scanf("%d",&elem);
            v[i]=elem%42;
        }
        sort(v.begin(),v.end());
        for(i=0;i<9;i++)
        {
                if(v[i]==v[i+1])
                {
                    countm--;
                }
        }
        printf("%d\n",countm);
    }
    return 0;
}
